iant functions. As a by-product we provide aconnexion between\ncomparison-based adaptive stochasticalgorithms and Markov chain Monte Carlo\nalgorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2013 06:54:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Nov 2013 16:54:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 25 Apr 2014 14:27:45 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 12 May 2014 14:11:34 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 4 Jan 2016 10:15:24 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2016 15:55:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-03"}
