 heavily damped as it propagates along the jet spire with\nspeeds of $\\sim110$ km/s. The magneto-seismological inversion of the wave\nparameters provides values of $B=1.21\\pm0.2$ G along the jet spire, which is in\nline with previous estimates for open fields in coronal holes.}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2013 15:58:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
